log
@remove .Tn; from Jan Stary <hans at stare dot cz>
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: caesar.6,v 1.8 2007/05/31 19:19:17 jmc Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 1989, 1991, 1993
.\"	The Regents of the University of California.  All rights reserved.
